## Acceptance

In order to get any license under these terms, you must agree to them as both strict obligations and conditions to all your licenses.

## Copyright License

The licensor grants you a copyright license for the software to do everything that would be infringed by one of your actions that is a copyright infringement, or a use of a copyright work for which you would be liable for copyright infringement, for any permitted purpose.

## Patent License

The licensor grants you a patent license for the software that would be infringed by one of your actions for any permitted purpose.

## Permitted Purposes

A permitted purpose is any noncommercial purpose.

## Noncommercial Purposes

A noncommercial purpose is any purpose that is not a commercial purpose.

## Commercial Purposes

A commercial purpose is any purpose that is intended for or directed toward commercial advantage or monetary compensation.

## Personal Purposes

Personal use of the software for your own noncommercial research, experimentation, and testing for the purpose of contributing to public knowledge, personal study, private entertainment, hobby projects, amateur pursuits, or religious observance are all noncommercial purposes, assuming they are not intended for or directed toward commercial advantage or monetary compensation.

## Limited Distribution and Changes

